To release a new build:
-----------------------

1. Update app version in the header of ./lib/indicator_sound_switcher/indicator.py
2. Update app version in the header of ./setup.py
3. Add change info into ./debian/changelog
4. Run ./build_package to build a source tarball and the accompanying files
5. Run the dput command displayed by build_package
6. Create snap: snapcraft clean && snapcraft snap
7. Upload snap: snapcraft upload --release=stable indicator-sound-switcher*.snap
